# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baip1.rpy:13
translate chinese baip1_4fa21f8f:

    # bai "Oof, probably telling my last girlfriend that I might be interested in guys."
    bai "哎，大概就是告诉前女友我可能对男生有兴趣那件事。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baip1.rpy:15
translate chinese baip1_ffbd6fca:

    # bai "I knew that the reaction was not going to be good, but I didn't expect her to completely turn against me and take all my friends with her."
    bai "我知道她的反应不会好，但没想到她会彻底与我决裂，还把我的朋友都带走了。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baip1.rpy:16
translate chinese baip1_d3859f56:

    # bai "I wish I would have just broken up with her and kept it a secret until I left for college."
    bai "真希望当初直接跟她分手，然后一直保密，直到我上大学为止。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baip1.rpy:18
translate chinese baip1_8b41827b:

    # bai "I don't know. I guess it helped me find who my real friends were… which was none of them."
    bai "我也不知道。我想这倒帮我认清了谁是真正的朋友……结果发现一个都没有。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baip1.rpy:20
translate chinese baip1_ddc15c60:

    # bai "I don't regret coming out, or at least partially coming out, but I regret doing it at that time."
    bai "我不后悔出柜，或者说至少不后悔部分出柜，但我后悔选在那个时候做这件事。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baip1.rpy:21
translate chinese baip1_e386481e:

    # bai "Should have waited until I was in a better place."
    bai "本该等到我处境更好时再做的。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baip1.rpy:23
translate chinese baip1_0d4610a1:

    # bai "Though I expect there would be drama no matter when I chose to do it."
    bai "不过我想，无论我什么时候选择出柜，恐怕都会闹得沸沸扬扬。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baip1.rpy:24
translate chinese baip1_9c2f65a6:

    # bai "It would have always been hard."
    bai "无论何时都会很艰难。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baip1.rpy:25
translate chinese baip1_8ac655b7:

    # pc "Well I'm here for you man, if you need support."
    pc "好吧，兄弟，如果你需要支持，我随时都在。"

# game/Scenes/Bai/BaiConversations/baip1.rpy:27
translate chinese baip1_ae9dc969:

    # bai "Thanks, man. I appreciate it."
    bai "谢谢，兄弟。我很感激。"

